  "detailed_description": "<i>I think I found my battle, Nam. - What? - My naval skirmish. </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709190/extras/8aca4301b4f403980cebb8e7ee61a540.poster.avif?t=1724776643\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709190/extras/8aca4301b4f403980cebb8e7ee61a540.webm?t=1724776643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709190/extras/8aca4301b4f403980cebb8e7ee61a540.mp4?t=1724776643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Help your love Dei make his own movie. Sell empanadas to fund the film or discover the dark origin of your relationship. <strong>HITM3</strong> is a third person, slice of life adventure where you control Nam on his days in Santiago de Chile. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709190/extras/2f7228653a73e86bcfcf7eba7d61c438.poster.avif?t=1724776643\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709190/extras/2f7228653a73e86bcfcf7eba7d61c438.webm?t=1724776643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709190/extras/2f7228653a73e86bcfcf7eba7d61c438.mp4?t=1724776643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Wake up each day with something different to do. Help with the movie or just buy a completo. <i>*Meow* Where did you come from?</i>  Share your loneliness with Dei, Astra, Belmo and Terco as your loving relationship is tested by the movie.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709190/extras/a1a3a89ec5654a5991f471c517868856.poster.avif?t=1724776643\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709190/extras/a1a3a89ec5654a5991f471c517868856.webm?t=1724776643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709190/extras/a1a3a89ec5654a5991f471c517868856.mp4?t=1724776643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br>- A soundtrack with tracks by Lia Nadja, Niñosindigo, Lavina Yelb, leorina, paltamango, Vicente Palma & mariapepinos.<br>- Reimagined movies from Raúl Ruiz, Shuji Terayama & Bruce LaBruce.<br>- 2 - 4 hours of gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709190/extras/f4ea477729443d3998d2bb621faba643.poster.avif?t=1724776643\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709190/extras/f4ea477729443d3998d2bb621faba643.webm?t=1724776643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709190/extras/f4ea477729443d3998d2bb621faba643.mp4?t=1724776643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
